{"type":"spell","name":"Gleam of the Freshly-Polished Glass","system":{"technique":{"value":"pe"},"form":{"value":"te"},"baseLevel":3,"range":{"value":"touch"},"duration":{"value":"moon"},"target":{"value":"room"},"complexity":0,"ritual":false,"technique-req":{"cr":false,"in":false,"mu":false,"pe":false,"re":false},"form-req":{"an":false,"aq":false,"au":false,"co":false,"he":false,"ig":false,"im":false,"me":false,"te":false,"vi":false},"description":"This spell maintains the equipment and tools of a lab in a constant state of immaculate cleanliness. Dirt, dust, and grime are all removed, leaving the outfittings positively gleaming, as if they had been freshly dusted and polished. This grants the Spotless Virtue to the lab, provided that the spell is cast every lunar month. If the spell ceases, the magus must maintain this pristine condition through more mundane means, otherwise the Virtue is lost. There is just one small drawback to this spell — the lab’s Warping score increases by one point (giving a Personality Trait Spotless +1) due to the unnatural nature of this cleaning, for as long as it is active.","source":"Cov","page":122,"indexKey":"gleam-of-the-freshly-polished-glass","targetSize":0,"enhancingRequisite":0,"general":false,"levelOffset":0,"baseEffectDescription":"","applyFocus":false,"bonus":0,"bonusDesc":"","xp":0,"masteryAbilities":"","review_status":"toReview","reviewer":"","ownership":null},"img":"systems/arm5e/assets/magic/te.png","effects":[],"flags":{},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"12.331","systemId":"arm5e","systemVersion":"2.3.2.5","createdTime":1730266623057,"modifiedTime":1730266623057,"lastModifiedBy":"6SdI10VpXHcBvx2J"},"_id":"VvWywucZRSrL2R1L","folder":"Cy6JvysNx2CNSwuF","sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0,"6SdI10VpXHcBvx2J":3}}
{"type":"spell","name":"Bridge of Wood","system":{"technique":{"value":"cr"},"form":{"value":"he"},"baseLevel":3,"range":{"value":"touch"},"duration":{"value":"sun"},"target":{"value":"ind"},"targetSize":2,"complexity":0,"ritual":false,"technique-req":{"cr":false,"in":false,"mu":false,"pe":false,"re":false},"form-req":{"an":false,"aq":false,"au":false,"co":false,"he":false,"ig":false,"im":false,"me":false,"te":false,"vi":false},"description":"Creates an ornate and exquisitely carved bridge made from living leaves, vines, and wood. The bridge can reach up to 20 paces, and is five paces wide. It is sturdy enough to support creatures of up to Size +4.","source":"ArM5","page":135,"indexKey":"bridge-of-wood","enhancingRequisite":0,"general":false,"levelOffset":0,"baseEffectDescription":"","applyFocus":false,"bonus":0,"bonusDesc":"","xp":0,"masteryAbilities":"","review_status":"toReview","reviewer":"","ownership":null},"img":"systems/arm5e/assets/magic/he.png","effects":[],"flags":{},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"12.331","systemId":"arm5e","systemVersion":"2.3.2.5","createdTime":1730266541909,"modifiedTime":1730266541909,"lastModifiedBy":"6SdI10VpXHcBvx2J"},"_id":"Vy1lhtaNHLzPdbhl","folder":"oUunfTgpdIKsTy19","sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0,"6SdI10VpXHcBvx2J":3}}
{"type":"spell","name":"The Master’s Message","system":{"technique":{"value":"re"},"form":{"value":"vi"},"baseLevel":1,"range":{"value":"touch"},"duration":{"value":"moon"},"target":{"value":"ind"},"complexity":0,"ritual":false,"technique-req":{"cr":false,"in":false,"mu":false,"pe":false,"re":false},"form-req":{"an":false,"aq":false,"au":false,"co":false,"he":false,"ig":false,"im":false,"me":false,"te":false,"vi":false},"description":"This spell opens a tunnel between the magus and a character that he touches.\nOnce it is cast, the tunnel remains in place, even if the characters break contact. The purpose of this spell is to enable the magus to open a tunnel between himself and a grog. The grog can then depart on a mission, and the magus is able to monitor his progress and cast spells through the tunnel as required.\nEven if the grog character has no Magic Resistance, it is a good idea to record the Penetration of this spell, as the grog may try to pass through a hostile Aegis.\nEffects cast through The Master’s Message tunnel can be up to one magnitude greater than the magnitude of The Master’s Message spell.","source":"HP","page":81,"indexKey":"the-masters-message","targetSize":0,"enhancingRequisite":0,"general":false,"levelOffset":0,"baseEffectDescription":"","applyFocus":false,"bonus":0,"bonusDesc":"","xp":0,"masteryAbilities":"","review_status":"toReview","reviewer":"","ownership":null},"img":"systems/arm5e/assets/magic/vi.png","effects":[],"flags":{},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"12.331","systemId":"arm5e","systemVersion":"2.3.2.5","createdTime":1730266633698,"modifiedTime":1730266633698,"lastModifiedBy":"6SdI10VpXHcBvx2J"},"_id":"W0MrgnoINdzJx0ut","folder":"FLOveJlX4MXFkepb","sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0,"6SdI10VpXHcBvx2J":3}}
{"type":"spell","name":"Seven-League Stride","system":{"technique":{"value":"re"},"form":{"value":"co"},"baseLevel":30,"range":{"value":"personal"},"duration":{"value":"moment"},"target":{"value":"ind"},"complexity":0,"ritual":false,"technique-req":{"cr":false,"in":false,"mu":false,"pe":false,"re":false},"form-req":{"an":false,"aq":false,"au":false,"co":false,"he":false,"ig":false,"im":false,"me":false,"te":false,"vi":false},"description":"Transports you to any place within seven leagues either that you can see or that you have an Arcane Connection with. If you fail an Intelligence + Finesse stress roll of 9+, your arrival goes slightly awry. For instance, you might fall when you appear, or just be facing the wrong way. A botch means you appear in the wrong place, perhaps even in a wall.\nPraefactus of Bonisagus’s version of this spell always allows him to appear in a safe, unembarrassing place (assuming he doesn’t fail his Finesse roll). All Praefactus’s spells make him seem as dignified as possible — manifesting his wizard’s sigil.","source":"ArM5","page":135,"indexKey":"seven-league-stride","targetSize":0,"enhancingRequisite":0,"general":false,"levelOffset":0,"baseEffectDescription":"","applyFocus":false,"bonus":0,"bonusDesc":"","xp":0,"masteryAbilities":"","review_status":"toReview","reviewer":"","ownership":null},"img":"systems/arm5e/assets/magic/co.png","effects":[],"flags":{},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"12.331","systemId":"arm5e","systemVersion":"2.3.2.5","createdTime":1730240398532,"modifiedTime":1730240398532,"lastModifiedBy":"6SdI10VpXHcBvx2J"},"_id":"W2WIZkJNLRYUYh4i","folder":"G2cgv5WjMszSYrBJ","sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0,"6SdI10VpXHcBvx2J":3}}
{"type":"spell","name":"Repose of the Eternal Moment","system":{"technique":{"value":"pe"},"form":{"value":"co"},"baseLevel":10,"range":{"value":"touch"},"duration":{"value":"year"},"target":{"value":"ind"},"complexity":0,"ritual":true,"technique-req":{"cr":false,"in":false,"mu":false,"pe":false,"re":false},"form-req":{"an":false,"aq":false,"au":false,"co":false,"he":false,"ig":false,"im":false,"me":false,"te":false,"vi":false},"description":"This ritual, which must be cast within the Magic Realm or by a character with Corpus Might, causes the target to disappear into the Twilight Void. As long as it lasts, it is as if he doesn’t exist; he will have no memory of the intervening time when, and if, he returns. Note that when the effect is cast in the Magic Realm, it is effectively permanent. A magus determined to ensure he no longer ages might use this effect on himself, first creating a vestige of himself that can be used as a link to draw him back.","source":"RoP:M","page":28,"indexKey":"repose-of-the-eternal-moment","targetSize":0,"enhancingRequisite":0,"general":false,"levelOffset":0,"baseEffectDescription":"","applyFocus":false,"bonus":0,"bonusDesc":"","xp":0,"masteryAbilities":"","review_status":"toReview","reviewer":"","ownership":null},"img":"systems/arm5e/assets/magic/co.png","effects":[],"flags":{},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"12.331","systemId":"arm5e","systemVersion":"2.3.2.5","createdTime":1730240398532,"modifiedTime":1730240398532,"lastModifiedBy":"6SdI10VpXHcBvx2J"},"_id":"W6gY5Do1AlObLIs8","folder":"G2cgv5WjMszSYrBJ","sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0,"6SdI10VpXHcBvx2J":3}}
