{"type":"spell","name":"The Laundress’ Clothesline","system":{"technique":{"value":"pe"},"form":{"value":"aq"},"baseLevel":4,"range":{"value":"personal"},"duration":{"value":"moment"},"target":{"value":"ind"},"complexity":0,"ritual":false,"technique-req":{"cr":false,"in":false,"mu":false,"pe":false,"re":false},"form-req":{"an":false,"aq":false,"au":false,"co":false,"he":false,"ig":false,"im":false,"me":false,"te":false,"vi":false},"description":"This spell immediately dries the caster’s clothing, which he must be wearing when this spell is cast.","source":"App","page":47,"indexKey":"the-laundress-clothesline","targetSize":0,"enhancingRequisite":0,"general":false,"levelOffset":0,"baseEffectDescription":"","applyFocus":false,"bonus":0,"bonusDesc":"","xp":0,"masteryAbilities":"","review_status":"toReview","reviewer":"","ownership":null},"img":"systems/arm5e/assets/magic/aq.png","effects":[],"flags":{},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"12.331","systemId":"arm5e","systemVersion":"2.3.2.5","createdTime":1730233430460,"modifiedTime":1730239446834,"lastModifiedBy":"6SdI10VpXHcBvx2J"},"_id":"nD7rJlXD3M9bB8Fu","folder":"U1PQp4E5HVBU8pTj","sort":300000,"ownership":{"default":0,"6SdI10VpXHcBvx2J":3}}
{"type":"spell","name":"The Thirsty Dagger","system":{"technique":{"value":"cr"},"form":{"value":"te"},"baseLevel":5,"range":{"value":"touch"},"duration":{"value":"moment"},"target":{"value":"ind"},"complexity":2,"ritual":true,"technique-req":{"cr":false,"in":false,"mu":false,"pe":false,"re":false},"form-req":{"an":false,"aq":false,"au":false,"co":false,"he":false,"ig":false,"im":false,"me":false,"te":false,"vi":false},"description":"This ritual creates a metal dagger. The blade contains cleverly designed gutters that feed into a reservoir in the hilt. This means that if anyone is injured by the dagger (takes a Wound), then a sample of their blood is collected in the dagger’s hilt. A version of this ritual could be created with as a spell with a duration (such as Sun) for use in emergency circumstances. However, the dagger created with the ritual is not magical, so it does not need to Penetrate Magic Resistance to harm a target (which a spell with a non-Momentary duration would need to do).\nThe dagger can be used as either a thrown or melee weapon. It is less useful in Defense than a normal dagger, and less aerodynamic than a throwing knife. In both cases, this is because The Thirsty Dagger is oddly weighted due to the blood reservoir. The dagger’s weapon characteristics are: .\nAbility: Brawl, Init: +0, Atk: +2, Dfn: -1, Dam: +3, Str: -1, Load: 0 .\nAbility: Thrown, Init: -1, Atk: 0, Dfn: -1, Dam: +2, Str: -1, Load: 0","source":"HP","page":88,"indexKey":"the-thirsty-dagger","targetSize":0,"enhancingRequisite":0,"general":false,"levelOffset":0,"baseEffectDescription":"","applyFocus":false,"bonus":0,"bonusDesc":"","xp":0,"masteryAbilities":"","review_status":"toReview","reviewer":"","ownership":null},"img":"systems/arm5e/assets/magic/te.png","effects":[],"flags":{},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"12.331","systemId":"arm5e","systemVersion":"2.3.2.5","createdTime":1730266623057,"modifiedTime":1730266623057,"lastModifiedBy":"6SdI