{"type":"spell","name":"Curse of the Werewolf","system":{"technique":{"value":"mu"},"form":{"value":"co"},"baseLevel":10,"range":{"value":"touch"},"duration":{"value":"year"},"target":{"value":"ind"},"complexity":1,"enhancingRequisite":1,"ritual":true,"technique-req":{"cr":false,"in":false,"mu":false,"pe":false,"re":false},"form-req":{"an":true,"aq":false,"au":false,"co":false,"he":false,"ig":false,"im":false,"me":true,"te":false,"vi":false},"description":"Over the course of a year, the target suffers from lycanthropy: the curse of the werewolf. With each full moon, the target transforms into the semblance of a wolf, losing both human body and mind to be replaced by lupine savagery. The effect goes beyond Hermetic understanding through the continued response to the moon without recourse to a device effect or linked trigger.\nThis effect is inspired by observing the repeated transformations of a werewolf.","source":"Dies","page":41,"indexKey":"curse-of-the-werewolf","targetSize":0,"general":false,"levelOffset":0,"baseEffectDescription":"","applyFocus":false,"bonus":0,"bonusDesc":"","xp":0,"masteryAbilities":"","review_status":"toReview","reviewer":"","ownership":null},"img":"systems/arm5e/assets/magic/co.png","effects":[],"flags":{},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"12.331","systemId":"arm5e","systemVersion":"2.3.2.5","createdTime":1730240398532,"modifiedTime":1730240398532,"lastModifiedBy":"6SdI10VpXHcBvx2J"},"_id":"nVve7ZYqY5pygXlS","folder":"G2cgv5WjMszSYrBJ","sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0,"6SdI10VpXHcBvx2J":3}}
